# Terminal Lab

Terminal command and local AI workflow lab for macOS Tahoe 26 on Apple Silicon.

## Defaults
- GitHub is the source of truth for docs, scripts, and container definitions.
- OrbStack is the default local Docker runtime on this workstation.
- Keep Docker CLI compatibility in commands and Compose files.
- Never commit secrets, `.env`, SSH keys, or `.zshenv`.

## Layout
- `docker/compose/` tracked local stacks
- `docker/env/` examples only, no real secrets
- `scripts/` helper wrappers
